        <h2>Internet Security &amp; Network Security</h2>

        <div class="two-col-text-img">
          <div>
            <p>Dr. Lavian offers <a href="/us-10598764-radar-target-detection-and-imaging-system-for-autonomous-car/">network security</a> technical consulting services involving Network security architecture, firewalls, VPNs, IPSec, Tunneling, Content Filtering, Security Gateways, IDS, and IPS. Network security is a component of any <a href="/communications-expert-witness/computer-networking-expert-witness/">computer networking</a> infrastructure. Dr. Lavian serves as a <a href="/">telecommunications expert witness</a> and <a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness/">internet expert witness</a> in network security matters.  Malware, stealthy network breaches, ransomware, and botnets have changed how we approach network security. Each network security layer implements policies and controls. Authorized users gain access to network resources, but malicious actors are blocked.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img loading="lazy" src="/images/content/network-security.jpg" alt="Network Security Expert"  width="1000" height="667"/>
